Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Cubic T-Matrix with Full Elastodynamic Green\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
Tensor", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"6180f57d-26a5-49db-89f1-cc8ee60b9555"],

Cell["T. M. Nestor \[Dash] Research School of Earth Sciences, ANU", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"395d7f45-2488-4578-8de2-9d7caff81f46"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["1. Setup and Green\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Tensor Definition", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"efb68b35-7d14-46ef-a7cd-7890f926b432"],

Cell["\<\
The elastodynamic Green\[CloseCurlyQuote]s tensor admits the radial \
decomposition G_ij(x) = f(r) \[Delta]_ij + g(r)/r^2 x_i x_j, with near-field \
(static 1/r), P-wave, and S-wave contributions.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"aa70d9c9-41da-4fd6-8e29-1c653319151c"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
ClearAll[\"Global`*\"]
xx = {x1, x2, x3};
rsq = x1^2 + x2^2 + x3^2;

(* Near-field constant *)
Cnf = (1 - \[Beta]^2/\[Alpha]^2)/(8 Pi \[Rho] \[Beta]^2);

(* P-wave and S-wave radial functions *)
Xr[r_] := Exp[I \[Omega] r/\[Alpha]]/(4 Pi \[Rho] \[Alpha]^2);
Vr[r_] := Exp[I \[Omega] r/\[Beta]]/(4 Pi \[Rho] \[Beta]^2);

(* f(r) and g(r) *)
fr[r_] := (Vr[r] - Cnf)/r;
gr[r_] := (3 Cnf + Xr[r] - Vr[r])/r;

(* Full Green's tensor *)
Gij[i_, j_] := fr[Sqrt[rsq]] KroneckerDelta[i, j] + gr[Sqrt[rsq]]/rsq xx[[i]] \
xx[[j]];

Print[\"Green's tensor defined.\"]\
\>", "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"2419a869-e6d3-4fb6-9079-ccd0ef5765b1"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"Green's tensor defined.\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.981834421280196*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"0f4acf97-0077-437b-ab6c-c13c4162500c"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["2. Taylor Expansion and Smooth Decomposition", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"2043ce8e-2e13-474e-927d-8ae13895201d"],

Cell["\<\
We expand f*r and g*r as Taylor series. The odd powers of r give the smooth \
polynomial part; the even powers give the singular (Eshelby) part.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"a73c73ff-0d1b-49e1-b8da-5f6ed99f7ad0"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Norder = 8;

(* f*r and g*r *)
frTimesR = Vr[r] - Cnf;
grTimesR = 3 Cnf + Xr[r] - Vr[r];

frSer = Series[frTimesR, {r, 0, Norder + 1}];
grSer = Series[grTimesR, {r, 0, Norder + 1}];

Print[\"f*r series:\"];
frSer\
\>", "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[20]:=",ExpressionUUID->"8f546235-30d8-41fc-b3aa-957bcfa147f0"],

